    printfn "ğŸ‰ CHATBOT UI INTEGRATION COMPLETE!"
    printfn ""
    printfn "ğŸ”§ Key Capabilities Demonstrated:"
    printfn "   âœ… Natural language UI command detection"
    printfn "   âœ… Automatic command translation (user intent â†’ CLI command)"
    printfn "   âœ… Autonomous UI system execution"
    printfn "   âœ… Intelligent response generation"
    printfn "   âœ… Error handling and user feedback"
    printfn ""
    printfn "ğŸ’¡ Users can now simply ask TARS to:"
    printfn "   â€¢ 'Start the UI' â†’ Autonomous UI system launches"
    printfn "   â€¢ 'Show me the interface' â†’ UI opens in browser"
    printfn "   â€¢ 'Evolve the UI' â†’ Interface adapts to current system state"
    printfn "   â€¢ 'What's the UI status?' â†’ System status report"
    printfn ""
    printfn "ğŸš€ TARS is now truly autonomous in UI management!"
    
    true
}

